<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>yeczunde<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Jacob
                                <expan>Topl<ex>er</ex>s</expan> und <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        geswistreid <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <add><expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan></add>, umb einen fride
                                <expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> in und
                        <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Hefel biz <app><note><q type="date">auf sant
                            <expan>Walp<ex>ur</ex>ge<ex>n</ex></expan> tag</q>01.05.1412</note></app> und
                                <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> tag bey ew <expan>cze
                                    süche<ex>n</ex></expan> <app><note><q type="date">auf den <expan>sunt<ex>ag</ex></expan>
<expan>reminisce<ex>re</ex></expan> schirst</q>28.02.1412</note></app>, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief und die abschrift
                            <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan> hören lassen und die
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns darauf geantwurt, sie
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> den fride also
                            <expan>halt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und den tag bey ew süchen. Wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> in <expan>sölich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lieb und <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan> möcht, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir auch allczeit <expan>sünderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Dorotee.</ab>
